(Direct/Convertee), Forest Section Officers (Promotee) and Forest Beat Officers (Direct) in the Academy. </p>

<p>During the training course apart from the faculty, senior officers of Forest Department (serving/retired), subject experts in various
 fields are invited from time to time to take up sessions mostly for the refresher trainings. </P>

